metadata.name: smolcoder #1
metadata.description: smolcoders is a collection of 500 NFTs hoping to raise funds to buy laptops for kids in need through LaptopDAO. 10% of all sales will be donated to LaptopDAO. If you want to help, collaborate with the org, or learn more, please visit https://laptopdao.org/. Project created by @javitoshi in December 2022.
